commit.message:
[BUGFIX][ENHANCEMENT] custom Data Docs errors with run_name filter; Data Docs auto-cleaning (#1786)

* Handle case where certain site sections undesired

* Adjust DefaultSiteIndexBuilder to only build site sections in config

* Add skip_and_clean_missing arg and functionality to index page builder

- if skip_and_clean_missing is True, when the index page is being built, any html pages without a corresponding source store key (e.g. a validation result html page without the corresponding validation result json) will be deleted and skipped (url won’t be added to index page)

* Add test for auto-cleaning ot DefaultSiteIndexBuilder

* Update changelog

* Linting

[BUGFIX][ENHANCEMENT] custom Data Docs errors with run_name filter; Data Docs auto-cleaning (#1786)

* Handle case where certain site sections undesired

* Adjust DefaultSiteIndexBuilder to only build site sections in config

* Add skip_and_clean_missing arg and functionality to index page builder

- if skip_and_clean_missing is True, when the index page is being built, any html pages without a corresponding source store key (e.g. a validation result html page without the corresponding validation result json) will be deleted and skipped (url won’t be added to index page)

* Add test for auto-cleaning ot DefaultSiteIndexBuilder

* Update changelog

* Linting
